ed as compared to\nthe previous method. Simulation results and experiment based on a wireless\nopen-access research platform under a practical wireless channel, show the\neffectiveness and superiority of the proposed method.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 06:45:57 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-29"}
