d demonstrate that the CNN+biLSTM is the best option when the\ncomputational complexity is not constrained, while when we restrict the\ncomplexity to lower levels, the three-layer perceptron provides the best\nperformance. Our complexity analysis for different NNs is generic and can be\napplied in a wide range of physical and engineering systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 08:47:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Jun 2021 08:44:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-10-13"}
