, for a short time, in a race with a photon.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 12:31:48 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 14 Jun 2021 07:23:15 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Mon, 30 Aug 2021 18:44:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-12"}
