r models. Expected shifts at the\nphotosphere are dominated by gravitational redshift, and are therefore\npredicted to be less than a few percent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Mar 2021 15:52:30 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-06-23"}
